<tmc-service-inc>
<pub id="RM21Q3EV">
<servcat id="43">
<name>BODY</name>
<section id="1002U_S0013" variety="S0013">
<name>WINDSHIELD / WINDOWGLASS</name>
<ttl id="1002U_S0013_7A835_T007J" variety="T007J">
<name>WINDOW DEFOGGER SWITCH</name>
<para id="RM000001OES00TX" category="G" type-id="8000T" name-id="WS0NW-01" from="201202">
<name>ON-VEHICLE INSPECTION</name>
<subpara id="RM000001OES00TX_01" type-id="01" category="01">
<s-1 id="RM000001OES00TX_01_0002" proc-id="RM21Q0EV__00002PN00000">
<ptxt>INSPECT REAR WINDOW DEFOGGER SWITCH ASSEMBLY</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="B085675E02" width="2.775699831in" height="2.775699831in"/>
</figure>
<s2>
<ptxt>Check the illumination area of the switch.</ptxt>
<spec>
<title>Standard measurement</title>
<table>
<tgroup cols="2">
<colspec colname="COL1" colwidth="2.07in"/>
<colspec colname="COL2" colwidth="2.06in"/>
<thead>
<row>
<entry>
<ptxt>Measurement Condition</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry>
<ptxt>Specified Condition</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>
<row>
<entry>
<ptxt>Battery positive (+) → 1 (ILL+)</ptxt>
<ptxt>Battery negative (-) → 2 (ILL-)</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry>
<ptxt>Illuminates</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</spec>
<ptxt>If the result is not as specified, replace the switch assembly.</ptxt>
<atten4>
<ptxt>The ON/OFF indicator of the switch will not illuminate.</ptxt>
</atten4>
</s2>
<s2>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="B085676E02" width="2.775699831in" height="2.775699831in"/>
</figure>
<ptxt>Check the ON/OFF indicator of the switch.</ptxt>
<s3>
<ptxt>Push the switch several times. Check that the ON/OFF indicator illuminates or turns off according to switch operation.</ptxt>
<spec>
<title>Standard measurement</title>
<table>
<tgroup cols="3">
<colspec colname="COL1" colwidth="1.38in"/>
<colspec colname="COLSPEC0" colwidth="1.38in"/>
<colspec colname="COL2" colwidth="1.37in"/>
<thead>
<row>
<entry>
<ptxt>Measurement Condition</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry>
<ptxt>Switch Condition</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry>
<ptxt>Specified Condition</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>
<row>
<entry>
<ptxt>Battery positive (+) → 5 (IG)</ptxt>
<ptxt>Battery negative (-) → 3 (E)</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry>
<ptxt>Defogger switch ON</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry>
<ptxt>Illuminates</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</spec>
<ptxt>If the result is not as specified, replace the switch assembly.</ptxt>
<atten4>
<ptxt>The illumination area of the switch will not illuminate.</ptxt>
</atten4>
</s3>
</s2>
<s2>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="B085677E01" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
<ptxt>Measure the resistance of the switch.</ptxt>
<spec>
<title>Standard resistance</title>
<table>
<tgroup cols="3">
<colspec colname="COL1" colwidth="1.38in"/>
<colspec colname="COLSPEC0" colwidth="1.38in"/>
<colspec colname="COL2" colwidth="1.37in"/>
<thead>
<row>
<entry>
<ptxt>Measurement Condition</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry>
<ptxt>Switch Condition</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry>
<ptxt>Specified Condition</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>
<row>
<entry>
<ptxt>4 (D) - 3 (E)</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry>
<ptxt>ON</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry>
<ptxt>Below 1 Ω</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row>
<entry>
<ptxt>4 (D) - 3 (E)</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry>
<ptxt>OFF</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry>
<ptxt>10 kΩ or higher</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</spec>
<ptxt>If the result is not as specified, replace the switch assembly.</ptxt>
</s2>
</content1>
</s-1>
</subpara>
</para>
</ttl>
</section>
</servcat>
</pub>
